00:06:29.899 --> 00:06:31.540
some thoughts too, so thank you,

00:06:31.540 --> 00:06:35.619
but Jeffrey said the pin name can be changed

00:06:35.619 --> 00:06:38.380
in the info tab of the pin on Connect,

00:06:39.579 --> 00:06:41.500
but he didn't know that you could change

00:06:41.500 --> 00:06:43.339
the parentheses name, though,

00:06:43.339 --> 00:06:45.500
as that's the path that it reads from.

00:06:47.339 --> 00:06:49.980
Yeah, and I'll add a, and again,

00:06:49.980 --> 00:06:52.019
interrupt me if my internet's getting all wonky,

00:06:52.019 --> 00:06:55.420
but naming things is very hard,

00:06:55.420 --> 00:06:58.100
and Pins is no exception to this.

00:06:59.380 --> 00:07:02.500
We actually hosted a workshop at conference

00:07:02.500 --> 00:07:04.339
where we did leverage Pins pretty heavily,

00:07:04.339 --> 00:07:07.299
and essentially every single person had their own pin.

00:07:07.299 --> 00:07:08.700
It was the exact same dataset,

00:07:08.700 --> 00:07:10.739
but they all had their own pin,

00:07:10.739 --> 00:07:13.579
and automatically it will append their,

00:07:13.579 --> 00:07:17.380
or preface their username to that pin name,

00:07:17.380 --> 00:07:19.540
and so when it's hosted on Connect,

00:07:19.540 --> 00:07:20.859
I mean, when you pin something,

00:07:20.859 --> 00:07:24.100
that is your piece of content on that Connect server,

00:07:24.100 --> 00:07:25.500
and Connect has a lot of advantages

00:07:25.500 --> 00:07:28.380
of being able to control access to other users,

00:07:28.380 --> 00:07:31.459
and so that is your, you are the owner of that content,

00:07:31.459 --> 00:07:34.220
so this concept of being able to change the name,

00:07:35.059 --> 00:07:36.899
it's not generally advisable,

00:07:36.899 --> 00:07:40.579
but we'd love to kind of learn about your use case

00:07:40.579 --> 00:07:42.859
on why you would wanna change the name,

00:07:42.859 --> 00:07:45.260
and so the Pins developer team,

00:07:45.260 --> 00:07:50.260
I spoke with Julia Silgi on this issue a lot,

00:07:50.500 --> 00:07:53.420
and we know we're not quite where we wanna be

00:07:53.420 --> 00:07:55.140
with the naming of Pins,

00:07:55.140 --> 00:07:57.019
and so if you have good use cases

00:07:57.019 --> 00:07:58.500
for why we might wanna change them,

00:07:58.500 --> 00:08:01.619
or make them more, less personal, so to speak,

00:08:01.619 --> 00:08:03.220
we'd love to hear that feedback.

00:08:05.220 --> 00:08:06.059
Yeah.

00:08:07.459 --> 00:08:08.299
Thank you.

