00:16:31.840 --> 00:16:36.840
So PINs, the nice thing about PINs is that it's a tool

00:16:37.400 --> 00:16:40.479
that's meant to be fairly, not just language agnostic,

00:16:40.479 --> 00:16:41.320
so you can actually,

00:16:41.320 --> 00:16:43.679
there's a PINs equivalent in Python as well,

00:16:43.679 --> 00:16:48.000
but also kind of where you want to pin things to.

00:16:48.000 --> 00:16:51.320
So within PINs, there's this concept of a board,

00:16:51.320 --> 00:16:53.320
and a board could be a variety of things.

00:16:53.320 --> 00:16:55.880
Now, within POSIT's professional tool chain,

00:16:55.880 --> 00:16:58.000
we really advocate for the use of POSIT Connect

00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:00.799
as that board, and it provides a lot of advantages

00:17:00.799 --> 00:17:04.040
because once it's pinned to POSIT Connect,

00:17:04.040 --> 00:17:05.680
it automatically is versioned.

00:17:05.680 --> 00:17:07.280
So if you have new versions of that PIN,

00:17:07.280 --> 00:17:09.000
you can just keep pinning to the same location

00:17:09.000 --> 00:17:11.959
over and over again, and access previous versions.

00:17:11.959 --> 00:17:13.439
But to speak to this question,

00:17:13.439 --> 00:17:15.760
when it's hosted on POSIT Connect,

00:17:15.760 --> 00:17:20.359
Connect has a really easy way to scope that PIN

00:17:20.359 --> 00:17:23.839
to a potential individual person.

00:17:23.839 --> 00:17:25.520
So if you wanna share it with just one other person,

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:26.520
you can do that.

00:17:26.520 --> 00:17:29.479
If you wanna share it with a group of individuals,

00:17:29.479 --> 00:17:33.400
so that group can be set up manually via Connect,

00:17:33.400 --> 00:17:34.319
or your administrators,

00:17:34.319 --> 00:17:36.040
or you can set up through your authentication

00:17:36.040 --> 00:17:37.400
that Connect is leveraging.

00:17:38.439 --> 00:17:41.880
So, and it's really kind of up to you

00:17:41.880 --> 00:17:43.359
in terms of who you wanna share it with,

00:17:43.359 --> 00:17:46.000
or what content you wanna share with on Connect.

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:47.680
So you have full control over that.

00:17:47.680 --> 00:17:51.199
But again, you can pin to other locations,

00:17:51.199 --> 00:17:52.760
and depending on where you pin that,

00:17:52.760 --> 00:17:55.160
if it's like some shared network drive

00:17:55.160 --> 00:17:56.599
internally that you have,

00:17:56.599 --> 00:17:58.160
that PIN will be essentially scoped

00:17:58.160 --> 00:18:00.079
to wherever it's living.

00:18:00.079 --> 00:18:01.239
So it's really kind of up to you.

00:18:01.239 --> 00:18:03.319
So PINs is pretty flexible in that manner.

00:18:05.319 --> 00:18:07.680
Thank you.

