00:19:30.319 --> 00:19:33.319
where the function may take like some text

00:19:33.319 --> 00:19:37.319
and then it spits out a response from an LLM.

00:19:37.319 --> 00:19:41.319
And so functions can actually absolutely be kind of,

00:19:41.319 --> 00:19:44.319
you know, served potentially through an API.

00:19:44.319 --> 00:19:47.319
That API can also be, you know,

00:19:47.319 --> 00:19:50.319
leveraged kind of using PINs in the background as well.

00:19:50.319 --> 00:19:53.319
So like, I think yes, the answer is yes,

00:19:53.319 --> 00:19:55.319
we can configure it.

00:19:55.319 --> 00:19:57.319
I'm not, I do not know for certain

00:19:57.319 --> 00:20:01.319
